### get all listings
GET http://localhost:8000/api/common/listings

### get listings with filters
GET http://localhost:8000/api/common/listings?category=Books&condition=Good

### get listings with search
GET http://localhost:8000/api/common/listings?search=maths

### get listings with price range
GET http://localhost:8000/api/common/listings?minPrice=100&maxPrice=500

### get single listing — replace id with real one
GET http://localhost:8000/api/common/listings/LISTING_ID_HERE

### get seller profile — replace id with real one
GET http://localhost:8000/api/common/seller/SELLER_ID_HERE